spec_data.Name: texlive-fontwrap
spec_data.Description:
The package (which runs under XeLaTeX) lets you bind fonts to
specific unicode blocks, for automatic font tagging of
multilingual text. The package uses Perl (via perltex) to
construct its tables.
spec_data.Signature: RSA/SHA256, Sun 06 Aug 2017 08:00:36 AM EDT, Key ID f55e7430f5282ee4
spec_data.Summary: Bind fonts to specific unicode blocks
